<paragraph id="74DBBBD04580E076E53955B57886E730" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
BRAZIL. Minas Gerais, Lagoa Santa, 
<emphasis id="A06924B1FE8D3CE6C03B9FD2C0985F68" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">E. Warming</emphasis>
